Master bed features a large vanity and walking closet. Spacious living room with fireplace. Two car garage. Large Oasis backyard that is simply breathtaking. Quick and easy freeway access and minutes from BART. top School district. NO HOA. 
This is your dream home come and take look! Assumable FHA loan .
